name: British Airways A380-841 [G-XLEF] Dusk Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
I was very glad to be able to see British Airways' A380 at YVR not once, but twice during my last trip to YVR in May 2016. Here we have G-XLEF making a slightly windy arrival on runway 26R as "Speedbird Five Victor Yankee Super". I've still got a couple more clips coming up from YVR, so stay tuned for those. Can't wait to go back sometime! Hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
